article.description: — Tommie Lewis had 15 points in Texas A&M-Commerce's 57-54 victory against Saint Joseph's on Friday night.
article.headline: Texas A&M-Commerce wins 57-54 over Saint Joseph's
article.linkText: Texas A&M-Commerce wins 57-54 over Saint Joseph's
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Tommie Lewis had 15 points in Texas A&M-Commerce's 57-54 victory against Saint Joseph's on Friday night. Lewis also contributed 10 rebounds and three steals for the Lions (2-4). Kalen Williams added nine points and he also had six rebounds. Alonzo Dodd had nine points and was 3 of 6 shooting and 3 of 4 from the free throw line. Lynn Greer III finished with 13 points for the Hawks (3-1). Xzayvier Brown added 11 points and seven rebounds for Saint Joseph's. Erik Reynolds II also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
